{
  "stem": "26728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I said, well, you better call your CO because I have people in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he let me in, and this-- me and this other guy and the jeep driver.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he took us to the towers, which was about every 50, 100 feet, let's say, wooden towers, all around the perimeter of the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And at about-- I'm going to guess-- 30%, 40% of the towers, there were SS troopers on the ground of the tow-- on the bottom of the towers, say 10 or 12 in each tower-- not every tower, but, but say 20% of the towers.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, this is where they had the big showdown with the 45th.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, the hell you say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, well, the scouts came in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The towers-- the, the-- one German officer and a Red Cross guy tried to surrender-- this was what they-- he told me, and some of this is in the book, some of it isn't.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These guys, these SS, decided to hell with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're going to have a shoot out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he fired-- somebody fired on these Americans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these guys had been in battle since Anzio.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are not to be trifled with, as I learned later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were hard ass infantry dog faces who had been from Anzio to Dachau-- casualty rates of over 50%.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and this was the 45th Division that I had been in in Fort Sill, Oklahoma, remember? 45th Thunderbird Division.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And saw the shoulder patches and the helmets that they have on some of them have decals on the helmet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I thought, Jesus, I've died and gone to heaven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Here I'm with the 45th again.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
